{"tid":471837,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［中国米製品］真係唔好食咁多米粉米線","createTime":"2017-11-17T15:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T09:26:14.000Z","uid":12449,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"491e2740247608ad86ed369fc02f29a95b46be0e","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"先唔講有啲餐廳會係渠邊處理食材<br />\n<br />\n同埋最近新聞驗到東莞米粉重金屬超標<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">原因有二個：</div><br />\n<br />\n你哋諗下米粉米線嘅唯二來源地 則係中国同台灣<br />\n<br />\n中国嘅米你哋未必會係日常生活接觸到<br />\n<br />\n但係由中国米轉化嘅米粉米線香港人就成人食<br />\n<br />\n但係啲鋪一定買最便最低質素嘅米粉米線去製作<br />\n<br />\n要來貨平 壓低成本 唔買台灣製造 係選擇<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">另外</div><br />\n<br />\n好多食客唔識分 以為彈牙白亮就最好<br />\n<br />\n不過 Sorry 呀 米線米粉係冇麵筋<br />\n<br />\n彈牙就一定係添加化學品<br />\n<br />\n自然嘅米係米白色 但你睇米粉米線？<br />\n<br />\n係白到偏藍嘅顏色<br />\n<br />\n點解呢啲店鋪會愈開愈多<br />\n<br />\n好明顯係因為米粉米線係中国米<br />\n<br />\n香港唔買中国米 淨係買泰國米<br />\n<br />\n咁唯有製成米製品 輸出香港<br />\n<br />\n利申：小市民 <br />\n<br />\n真係唔知香港人對米粉米線嘅消耗<br />\n<br />\n比起係白米係幾多成 <br />\n<br />\n但中国米製品真係少食為妙"},{"pid":"e4f5ba6ae7216e76f217d1a617957080c8069fdd","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"我食過手工米線米線<br />\n<br />\n 啲色雖然冇出票餐廳咁白<br />\n<br />\n帶米白<br />\n<br />\n但係泰國米無化學添加做<br />\n<br />\n食落都安心好多"},{"pid":"dc59e5e8b498ec552b4e2a703c8175eedf63218f","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"隨時麥記啲過期肉都安全過米粉米線"},{"pid":"be2b4df71716b6c5e38588f04503dbc042ae5fd2","tid":471837,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"譚仔呢？"},{"pid":"e6f2ea13c8f57153883ceda5f75c5050d1541144","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譚仔呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估佢啲米線唔係中国米咩？"},{"pid":"025d53f172ed5836f977712b74d50ef848f507c1","tid":471837,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:11:05.000Z","msg":"食米線=狗"},{"pid":"0ece5d8ddb3993dabb093b2b2e255949c8f10d4d","tid":471837,"uid":124471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譚仔呢？</blockquote><br />\n連亞姐都9係大陸新移民，食村材唔通同你用美國咩。<br />\n<br />\n係連登仔呢間野先話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523fc015f13752d8de9b5d700eac9433bea700f3","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>譚仔呢？</blockquote><br />\n連亞姐都9係大陸新移民，食村材唔通同你用美國咩。<br />\n<br />\n係連登仔呢間野先話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以香港人普遍係跟風冇腦<br />\n<br />\n辣味已經係化學添加會患癌<br />\n<br />\n連抗拒食用嘅中国米轉咗個樣都唔知"},{"pid":"ee3b27e5c502516ade87d7b0cf23ac131682ee50","tid":471837,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"用膠做"},{"pid":"ad39cef6148b756ff50c36953d41990e283d76e4","tid":471837,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用膠做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衰啲嘅可能唔用米整"},{"pid":"27e7f551d596f84a3bf19493c3d61ba4120d959b","tid":471837,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"Double line spacing"}]}